      • canFill

        public boolean canFill()
        从接口复制的说明: IFluidTankProperties
        Returns true if the tank can be filled at any time (even if it is currently full). It does not consider the contents or capacity of the tank. This value is constant. If the tank behavior is more complicated, returns true.
        指定者:
        canFill 在接口中 IFluidTankProperties

      • canDrain

        public boolean canDrain()
        从接口复制的说明: IFluidTankProperties
        Returns true if the tank can be drained at any time (even if it is currently empty). It does not consider the contents or capacity of the tank. This value is constant. If the tank behavior is more complicated, returns true.
        指定者:
        canDrain 在接口中 IFluidTankProperties

      • canFillFluidType

        public boolean canFillFluidType(FluidStack fluidStack)
        从接口复制的说明: IFluidTankProperties
        Returns true if the tank can be filled with a specific type of fluid. Used as a filter for fluid types. Does not consider the current contents or capacity of the tank, only whether it could ever fill with this type of fluid. FluidStack is used here because fluid properties can depend on NBT, the amount is ignored.
        指定者:
        canFillFluidType 在接口中 IFluidTankProperties

Does not consider the current contents or capacity of the tank, only whether it could ever drain out this type of fluid. FluidStack is used here because fluid properties can depend on NBT, the amount is ignored.
